name: Sob Muffling Sound Baffles - An Eat The Babies collection
description:
Here's some of the best Eat the Babies strips from the first two years, corrected and collected into one paper volume that will last till the end of time. Or at least till the end of you. 

Make sure your children can read about depressed monsters under the bed and obscure economic theories described by humanoids with appliances for faces.

20 pages. B&W. Photocopied. White pages inside.

name: Good For America!
description:
The Darkest Political Mini-comic of 2012! Good for America follows a blatheringly insane, Ayn Rand style Capitalist as he espouses his bat$%*# crazy philosophy on thru a revised history version of the 2012 election.

Prepare to get offended. And to transcend.

16 pages. Glossy paper. Digitally printed. B&W inside.
